concrete classda asla abstract method creat edýlmez
4-abstract býr class da hem abstract gem de cýncrete methd olabýlýr 
5- cýncrete class abstract classa extend edýldugunde abstract classtaju tum abstract methodlarý ýmplement etmek zorundadýr ama concrete methodlarý ýmplement yapmayabýlýr

6- bir abstract class baska býr classsa extend edýldýgýnde herhangý býr mrhou overrýde etmek zorunda degýl 
cunku javaya gore abstaract chýld classýnda latýnda möutlaka concrete býr chýld lass vardýr
